      <title>市场崩盘加剧 英国 10 年期国债收益率创 2008 年以来新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/uk-prepares-to-sell-new-five-year-bonds-as-borrowing-costs-surge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国市场暴跌，债券收益率升至十多年来的最高水平，对持续通胀压力的担忧引发了与 2022 年英国政府债券危机令人不安的对比。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/uk-prepares-to-sell-new-five-year-bonds-as-borrowing-costs-surge</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 09:14:36 GMT</pubDate>
